Time_Stamp.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.opportunitysplits_revinsights.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = group q by all; q = foreach q generate toString(now(), "yyyy/MM/dd") as 'today_date';

time_series_with_forecast.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.opportunitysplits_revinsights.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by 'Opportunity.ForecastCategory' == "Closed"; k = group q by all; k = foreach k generate "2000" as 'Date_Year', "01" as 'Date_Month', "01" as 'Date_Day'; k = group k by ('Date_Year', 'Date_Month', 'Date_Day'); k = foreach k generate 'Date_Year', 'Date_Month', 'Date_Day', count() as 'sum'; k = fill k by (dateCols=('Date_Year','Date_Month','Date_Day', "Y-M-D")); k = timeseries k generate 'sum' as 'cnt' with (length=10000,  dateCols=('Date_Year','Date_Month','Date_Day', "Y-M-D")); k = filter k by {{row(CloseDate_1.selection, [0], ["min", "max"]).asDateRange("date('Date_Year','Date_Month', 'Date_Day')")}}; k = filter k by date('Date_Year','Date_Month', 'Date_Day') in [.."current day"]; k = group k by all; k1 = foreach k generate first('Date_Year') as 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Year', first('Date_Month') as 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Month', first('Date_Day') as 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Day', 0 as 'A'; k2 = foreach k generate last('Date_Year') as 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Year', last('Date_Month') as 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Month', last('Date_Day') as 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Day'; k3 = union k1,k2; a = group q by ('Opportunity.CloseDate_Year', 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Month', 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Day'); a = foreach a generate 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Year', 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Month', 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Day', sum(q.'${Variables.OpportunitySplit_Amount.fieldName}') as 'A'; c = union a,k3; c = foreach c generate 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Year', 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Month', 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Day', 'A'; c = fill c by (dateCols=('Opportunity.CloseDate_Year','Opportunity.CloseDate_Month','Opportunity.CloseDate_Day', "Y-M-D")); c = filter c by date('Opportunity.CloseDate_Year','Opportunity.CloseDate_Month', 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Day') in [.."current day"]; result = group c by ('Opportunity.CloseDate_Year', 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Month', 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Day'); result = foreach result generate c.'Opportunity.CloseDate_Year' + "~~~" + c.'Opportunity.CloseDate_Month' + "~~~" + c.'Opportunity.CloseDate_Day' as 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Year~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Month~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Day', first('A') as 'A'; result = group result by 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Year~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Month~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Day'; result = foreach result generate 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Year~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Month~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Day', first(A) as 'A', sum(sum(A)) over ([..0] partition by all order by ('Opportunity.CloseDate_Year~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Month~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Day')) as 'Cumulative_Amount'; result = order result by ('Opportunity.CloseDate_Year~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Month~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Day' asc); start_forecast = group result by all; start_forecast = foreach start_forecast generate last('Opportunity.CloseDate_Year~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Month~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Day') as 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Year~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Month~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Day', last('Cumulative_Amount') as 'Cumulative_Amount'; start_forecast = foreach start_forecast generate case when 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Year~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Month~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Day' < "{{cell(intermediate_date_step.result, 0, "start_day").asString()}}" then "{{cell(intermediate_date_step.result, 0, "start_day").asString()}}" else 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Year~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Month~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Day' end as 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Year~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Month~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Day', 'Cumulative_Amount'; a1 = load "${App.Datasets.opportunitysplits_revinsights.FullyQualifiedName}"; a1 = group a1 by all; end_forecast = foreach a1 generate "{{cell(intermediate_date_step.result, 0, "end_day").asString()}}" as 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Year~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Month~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Day', {{coalesce(cell(saql_commit.result, 0, "sum_${Variables.OpportunitySplit_Amount.fieldName}"),0).asString()}} as 'Cumulative_Amount'; forecast_line = union start_forecast, end_forecast; final = group result by 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Year~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Month~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Day' full, forecast_line by 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Year~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Month~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Day'; final = foreach final generate coalesce(result['Opportunity.CloseDate_Year~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Month~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Day'], forecast_line['Opportunity.CloseDate_Year~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Month~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Day']) as 'Opportunity.CloseDate_Year~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Month~~~Opportunity.CloseDate_Day', first(result['Cumulative_Amount']) as 'Closed Won Sales', last(forecast_line['Cumulative_Amount']) as 'Commit Forecast';

Team_Performance_AvgKPI3.query: user = load "${App.Datasets.userrole_revinsights.FullyQualifiedName}"; opp = load "${App.Datasets.opportunitysplits_revinsights.FullyQualifiedName}"; closed_won = filter opp by 'Opportunity.IsWon' == "true"; closed_total = filter opp by 'Opportunity.IsClosed' == "true"; commit = filter opp by 'Opportunity.ForecastCategory' in ["Forecast", "Closed"]; best_case = filter opp by 'Opportunity.ForecastCategory' in ["BestCase", "Forecast", "MostLikely", "Closed"]; open_pipe = filter opp by 'Opportunity.ForecastCategory' in ["BestCase", "Forecast", "MostLikely", "Pipeline"]; activities = load "${App.Datasets.Activity.FullyQualifiedName}"; completed_activities = filter activities by 'Status' == "Completed"; open_activities = filter activities by ('Status' != "Completed" || 'Status' is null); overdue_activities = filter activities by 'IsOverdue' == "true" && ('Status' != "Completed" || 'Status' is null); c = group user by all full,  closed_won by all full,  closed_total by all full,  commit by all full,  best_case by all full,  open_pipe by all full,  completed_activities by all full,  open_activities by all full,  overdue_activities by all; c = group c by all; c = foreach c generate {{cell(team_selector_3.selection,0, "projection_kpi").asObject()}};

relative_urls.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.opportunitysplits_revinsights.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = group q by all; q = foreach q generate "/lightning/page/forecasting?c__forecastingTypeId=" + "12345678" + "&c__forecastingOwnerId=" + "{{cell(intermediate_step.result, 0, "Id").asString()}}" as 'forecasting_url',  "{{valueAt(coalesce(cell(CloseDate_1.selection, 0, "min"), "fiscal_quarter"),0).asString()}}" as 'date_range',  "{{valueAt(coalesce(cell(CloseDate_1.selection, 0, "min"), "fiscal_quarter"),1).asString()}}" as 'date_offset',  count() as 'count'; q = foreach q generate 'forecasting_url', 'date_range', 'date_offset', 'count', case       when 'date_range' == "fiscal_quarter" && 'date_offset' == "1"              then "NEXT_FISCAL_QUARTER"       when 'date_range' == "month"  && 'date_offset' == "1"              then "NEXT_MONTH"      when 'date_range' == "month"              then "THIS_MONTH"      else              "THIS_FISCAL_QUARTER"  end  as 'date_literal', case       when 'date_range' == "fiscal_quarter"         then "quarter"     when 'date_range' == "month"         then "month"      else         "quarter"  end  as 'date_period', case       when 'date_offset' == "-1"         then "0"     when 'date_offset' == "0" && 'date_range' == "fiscal_quarter"         then number_to_string(daysBetween(now(), fiscal_quarter_last_day(now()))+1,"##0")     when 'date_offset' == "0" && 'date_range' == "month"         then number_to_string(daysBetween(now(), month_last_day(now()))+1,"##0")     when 'date_offset' == "1" && 'date_range' == "fiscal_quarter"         then number_to_string(daysBetween(toDate(date_to_epoch(fiscal_quarter_last_day(now()))+86400), toDate(date_to_epoch(fiscal_quarter_last_day(toDate(date_to_epoch(fiscal_quarter_last_day(now()))+86400)))+86400)),"##0")     when 'date_offset' == "1" && 'date_range' == "month"         then number_to_string(daysBetween(toDate(date_to_epoch(month_last_day(now()))+86400), toDate(date_to_epoch(month_last_day(toDate(date_to_epoch(month_last_day(now()))+86400)))+86400)),"##0")     else         number_to_string(daysBetween(now(), fiscal_quarter_last_day(now()))+1,"##0") end  as 'days_remaining';
